endsnippet

snippet h3 "Create a H3 heading."
### ${1:title}
endsnippet

snippet h4 "Create a H4 heading."
#### ${1:title}
endsnippet

snippet h5 "Create a H5 heading."
##### ${1:title}
endsnippet

snippet h6 "Create a H6 heading."
###### ${6:title}
endsnippet

snippet i "italic"
_${1:text}_
endsnippet

snippet b "bold"
**${1:text}**
endsnippet

